===Etymology===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*srjal||to breed; to bring up}}, whence {{cog|bo|སྲེལ||to bring up; to rear}}.

{{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}} notes that this word is equally likely to have been {{der|zh|aav}} in origin. Compare {{cog|km|សំរាល||to give birth}}.

